    <div class="uk-card uk-card-default uk-card-hover">
        <div class="uk-card-media-top uk-cover-container" style="min-height: 300px;">
            <img src="/media/images/2020/03/verbatlas_logo_square_512.jpg" uk-cover>
        </div>

        <div class="uk-card-body">
            <h3 class="uk-card-title">VerbAtlas is now out!</h3>
            <p>We are proud to announce that VerbAtlas 1.0 <a href="http://verbatlas.org" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">(verbatlas.org)</a> is finally available for <a href="http://verbatlas.org/download" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">download</a>.
<br/>
Developed at the <a href="http://nlp.uniroma1.it">Sapienza NLP group</a>, the multilingual Natural Language Processing group at the Sapienza University of Rome, VerbAtlas is a novel large-scale manually-crafted semantic resource for wide-coverage, intelligible and scalable Semantic Role Labeling. The goal of VerbAtlas is to manually cluster WordNet synsets that share similar semantics into a set of semantically-coherent frames.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="uk-card-footer">
            <a href="/posts/2" class="uk-button uk-button-text"><span class="uk-margin-small-right" uk-icon="icon: plus"></span>Read more</a>
        </div>
